\begin{theorem} [Existence and Uniqueness Theorem for Nonlinear Dynamical Systems]
\label{thm:exist_unique_jump}
Consider the nonlinear dynamical system defined by \eqref{eq:3.9}. If the following conditions hold, the system is guaranteed to exhibit chaotic behavior for all $t$.

